    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept older car in good overall condition and a solid choice for someone looking for a nice driver rather than a full project. It presents well for its age, with the kind of light cosmetic wear and minor imperfections you\u2019d expect on an older vehicle, but nothing that takes away from it being an enjoyable, usable example. A buyer should expect a car that has been maintained and remains presentable, while still showing some age in places if you look closely. Overall, this is an honest, good-condition car that should suit someone who wants a classic to drive and improve gradually if desired.",
